texts.text: Great. Now where'd they go? We don't have time for this.
>After the battle, the band of people you rescued suddenly dispersed,
>going their separate ways saying somebody is calling to them.
During the fight, those people looked like they were being controlled. Like puppets on a string
It probably has something to do with this Aura Gate...
That's no excuse. Not when I'm going out of my way to help them okay?
And you have no way to prove they're being manipulated.
Whoa. Just chill out a bit, Shionyan.
*Sigh* This is the worst.
Yo, don't be like that.
Although I guess we'd have to go look for 'em.
People that can't fight are being made to fight, we can't just leave them like that. It's too dangerous man.
>Just then, you hear the sound of fighting coming from somewhere close by...!
Well speak of the devil... Let's go guys!

Eeeek!
*Cower*
Oh, it's that middle aged guy again...
Look at his movements! It definitely looks like he's being controlled like a puppet!
And look over there!
Ya! Take that!
It's the guy in the hood!
...He's improved a bit. But judging from his motions, he's hurt.
>On the ground near the men are what looks to be splatters of human blood.
Then there's no room for error this time!
Right on it!
You don't need to tell me!
Bow before me, weaklings! Do not burden yourself with being a hero!
Shit, these demons are even tougher than the last batch!
If you have the time to complain, move your ass and fight!
Yeah but...
E-Eeeek! I don't wanna...!

*Pant*
*Groan*
>The condition of the two men fighting barehanded is getting worse by the minute...
It's hard to fight protecting these two!
Ugh... Dammit!
Our only hope is to break through and try to get to the others.
We need an opening...
Megakin! Watch out!
>Scouting for a way out, Megakin does not see the demon attacking him from behind.
>Shiang Sun uses his own demon to save Megakin, just in the nick of time.
Thanks for the save, Chalk Eater!
I'll cover your back! Find us a way outta here!
...Ahhh, I see.
Whoaaaa!!
>Suddenly, the demons start to focus their attacks on the middle aged man...!
W-What the hell? Why am I being targeted?!
They've caught on to us! These demons are smart!
Underhanded pricks! I'm going to kill them all...!
Please... No more. Please...
Stupid idiot! Why are we even...
No time to complain remember?!
But man, things ain't lookin' very...
Oh shit!
>A moment's distraction was all it took, and now the demon that broke through is about to kill the middle aged man.
No-Nooooooo!!
Not on my watch!
Oof!
Arrrrgh!
*Cough*
Taking a hit to save another guy huh? You think you're some kind of hero?
Well this is the end of the line for you, wanna be hero!
Shit! They're too far....
Ugh...!
*Roar*
Huh?
Oof!
Aaaaargh!
>The middle aged man who was pushed out of harm's way gets right back up and
>pushes the young man back, taking the blow himself.
What are you doin' man?!
...Megakin, we have to get rid of these demons first! We have to end this!
I know... I know goddammit!
Hey mister! Mister!

Heh...Ouch...
Stop shaking me, it hurts.
Why... Why did you push me out of the way...?
Well, it's twice I owe you now,
thought I'd at least pay you back once.
But you... You said you didn't want to fight...
That's right...
But that demon called you a hero...
That kinda got me jealous...
When I was a kid, I wanted to be a hero too... To help people...
You know, to fight for justice and stuff......
This should... bring me a bit closer to that dream...
Being a hero...
>The man's body goes limp, his arms dangling down lifelessly...
Hey mister...! Hey!
Talk to me goddammit.. C'mon!
>The middle aged man's body dissipates into light.
...Sorry man. That's the second time we failed to protect you people.
N-No... If you hadn't come, I'd be dead too...
What do we do now? If we bring this guy along, he might just run off again...
Please, take me with you.
Take you with us? Who's fault do you think it is that we're here in the first place?
It's nobody's fault, aight Shionyan? You know that.
Yes, I know that, but does he?
If he doesn't, then he's going to do something stupid and get someone else killed. That's why I'm asking.
...We don't know if we can protect you all the way man.
Especially if you lose control and run off again.
What do you say to that?
I don't know how I can get you to trust me on this, but I don't think it will happen again.
And you know this because...?
When I decided that there's no option but to fight, the feeling of being controlled by someone disappeared.
Maybe it's too late, but I've made up my mind and I'm ready for whatever may come. So please take me with you.
What? Do you expect us to believe this gung-ho theory of yours?
...Actually, it might be plausible.
You too Shiang...? Is everyone mad?
I'm perfectly normal.
It's just a theory,
but I think this manipulation thing is something that forces people to fight against their will.
Oh! So if you're willing to fight in the first place, then it has no hold over you.
Well, I don't think we have another choice anyway, so we might as well believe him.
Believe him. Right...
Aight, we should meet up with the others and head towards the center of this place.
So your heroics won't be in vain, right?
